{
  "stem": "13096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, as I say, we were in these villages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't even hear any bomb-- bombs anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were just even trying to, you know, to have a normal life again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as we had a little bit of money, we didn't worry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't go anymore to our houses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We left it everything there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But prior to this, you know, going to the villages, everybody in Rhodes Island, you know-- they had a little bit of gold hiding away for better days, you know, for rainy days.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because in those times, nobody believe in the banks-- you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, you-- everybody, when you save a little bit of money, you put in the saving account.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You do this and that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There, you know, they had-- they believe in buying coins, gold coins, little bit of jewelry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Even the poorest people, they had some gold things with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it means, you know, we all had buried in our houses very precious things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when later on, the Germans came and collected our jewelry-- I'll tell you just in between-- they never, in there, you know, their wild dream, expected to find so much precious things in a small island with a small population of not so rich people-- in Rhodes Island.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyhow, we were in-- in-- in the villages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And on the 19 of July, 1944, you know, the Germans, they were send the two-- two SS from Athens, from the Gestapo, to come to Rhodes Island, and to liquidate the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were two brothers in the-- who had-- Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "One, he was, Costa Ekinati.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was like an interpreter who would speak very good German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he came with two Jewish-- two German officers to Rhodes Island.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
